2. &lt;a href=&quot;http://radar.oreilly.com/2012/07/data-jujitsu.html&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;資料柔術（Data Jujitsu）&lt;/a&gt;,last visited 06/14/2013.&lt;/p&gt;

